Cosmic Flight is a fast paced adventure game in which you fly a small craft through a dangerous
galaxy, collecting as much energy as possible and avoiding danger.
As you get more energy, you gain more powerful weapons but the game becomes more difficult.

Controls:
'A' = Move Left
'D' = Move Right
Space = Fire

This program requires the MikeOS BASIC interpreter. It may not work on MikeOS derivative or OS
independent versions of the MikeOS BASIC interpreter.

Files:
cf.bas - The runable program
CHANGES - Information about updates to this program
COPYING - GNU GPLv3 Licence used for this program
INSTALL - Instructions on how to use this program
README - This file

